<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ supportTeam }} - Two-Factor Authentication Disabled</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #080D4A; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; color: #4A5568; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<div style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 448px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="background-color: #7BBA29; color: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;">
                Two-Factor Authentication Disabled
            </h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #4A5568;">
                Hello {{ uuid }},
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4A5568; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                We wanted to inform you that your Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) has been disabled by an administrator.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4A5568; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                If this action was unexpected or unauthorized, please contact our support team immediately for
                assistance.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4A5568; margin-top: 2rem;">
                For your safety, we recommend re-enabling Two-Factor Authentication at the earliest opportunity.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #4A5568; margin-top: 1rem;">
                Please access the following link to manage your Two-Factor Authentication settings:
            </p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #718096;">
                Support team:
                <a href="mailto:{{ contactEmail }}"
                   style="color: #0045AD; text-decoration: underline;">{{ contactEmail }}</a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #718096;">
                Thank you,<br>
                <strong>{{ supportTeam }} Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
